|source 1 = NOAA（1981–2010年相对湿度；1961–1990年日照）<ref name = "NWS Dickinson, TX">{{cite web |url = https://www.weather.gov/wrh/climate?wfo=hgx |title = NowData - NOAA Online Weather Data |publisher = [[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] |accessdate = 2022-01-02 |dead-url = no |archive-date = 2022-04-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220401232806/https://www.weather.gov/wrh/climate?wfo=hgx }}</ref><ref name="1991-2020 normals">{{cite web |format=csv |url=https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/access/services/data/v1?dataset=normals-monthly-1991-2020&startDate=0001-01-01&endDate=9996-12-31&stations=USW00012960&format=csv |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |title=Station: HOUSTON INTERCONT AP, TX US USW00012960 |access-date=2021-05-05 |archive-date=2022-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220128044340/https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/access/services/data/v1?dataset=normals-monthly-1991-2020&startDate=0001-01-01&endDate=9996-12-31&stations=USW00012960&format=csv |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name= noaasun >{{cite web | url = ftp://ftp.atdd.noaa.gov/pub/GCOS/WMO-Normals/TABLES/REG_IV/US/GROUP3/72243.TXT  | title = WMO Climate Normals for HOUSTON/INTERCONTINENTAL, TX 1961–1990 | accessdate = 2014-03-10 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration}}</ref><ref name="RH">{{cite web |url = https://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/data/lcd/annual/2018/01201813IAH.pdf |title = Local Climatological Data Annual Summary with Comparative Data for HOUSTON, TEXAS (KIAH) |publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |access-date = 2022-06-11 |page=3}}</ref><br/>
休斯顿官方气象站，1888年7月–1969年5月在市中心的气象局，1969年6月起在洲际机场。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://threadex.rcc-acis.org/ |title=ThreadEx |access-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060519074347/http://threadex.rcc-acis.org/ |archive-date=2006-05-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
